{"tid":1380622,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日一篇]洗唔撚洗每日講一次呀","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:58:26.000Z","uid":38923,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87228db9608c15826c165073f33b4349a78c925f","tid":1380622,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家就係要日撚日講 不割蓆 不篤灰 唔好再同我講乜撚野依樣唔啱果樣唔啱</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>既然係向住同一個目標進發嘅 點解唔一齊行落去 而要係到屌嚟屌去?? 屌到散撚哂</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要知道 和理非係示威者嘅盾 勇武係示威者嘅劍 兩者缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"31ec38b176ad27322d4e97d90336f0c77f57ad1b","tid":1380622,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52cb76220f5ad3120aa0b05b53f9da21ae9b28e6","tid":1380622,"uid":156632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足<br />\n呢場運動之所以仲繼續到落去全賴大家學識不割蓆 所以唔好被輕易帶動<br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n遇到啲講錯嘢嘅手足要予以糾正 以防更多人受影響<br />\n</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n遇到三毛 上一頁 唔好推唔好負評有佢沉 <br />\n三毛特癥：<br />\n-禁入個po冇內容可言/得幾隻字<br />\n-標題黨<br />\n-p牌<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰只係理念唔係絕對 唔好俾呢樣嘢騎劫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cd924cc203b6d57001930e29634a4e3b5e43f10","tid":1380622,"uid":38923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"大家小心三毛搞分化<br />\n班畜牲咁撚廢<br />\n一眼都睇得出啦<br />\n連登仔要煉成金睛火眼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a7315773a481af88e169b46aec597df057d3f","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"23d62447e037f3102cf2257dab9bfe88457e9410","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"96816daf6ca901bd929fd6825c435d8dbb6e9657","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4b5b84f41a449ba8f2c71736fac2263bec3a984b","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"476185492d6c758a79a481fac8045084c4474949","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5e33b755c9ea5a5c201d35491e7556df980c7c44","tid":1380622,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5號齊罷工</strong></